template(name="md_collapse__demo")
  .component-title MD Collapse
  p.docs
    | An MD Collapse generates a collapsible text container that is used to
    | conceal the major portion of text in the container until a toggle button
    | is clicked to reveal it. In the demo that follows, the Lorem Ipsum text is
    | placed in a collapsible text container. Click the toggle button to reveal/
    | hide text.
  .demo-box
    .demo-group
      .demo--collapse
        +md_collapse(
          content="lorem_ipsum"
        )
  p.docs The above collapsible text container is generated by the code below.
  +doc_box(
    id="doc-box--md-collapse"
    id__tabs="md-collapse__tabs"
    tabs=tabs
    name__spacebars="md-collapse__spacebars"
    name__jade="md-collapse__jade"
    code__spacebars=code__spacebars
    code__jade=code__jade
    api_screen="MD Collapse API"
  )

